These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, pilot, accountant, videographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the accountant is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the accountant##6
5. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
6. the engineer is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | videographer  | engineer | accountant | pilot  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, scientific, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person watching disaster movies##7
6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| Movie-Genre    | scientific      | romance | disaster | crime |

