.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra, fonseca, blend
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the alhambra-smoker##8
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
5. the fan of blues is the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Cigar         | alhambra | blend | fonseca | tiparillo |

