.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, romance, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, yellow, green, red
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##7
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##7
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
5. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who likes yellow##7
6. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the person who likes yellow is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
8. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | romance | scientific | epic    |
| Color         | lavender | red   | green   | yellow |

