.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil, iris, dahlia
1. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who growsiris##7
3. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
4. the person who growsdahlia is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
5. the person who growsdahlia is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Flower      | marigold | iris | dahlia  | daffodil |

