.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, entrepreneur, project-manager
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, canasta, bridge
1. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Game   | billiard   | canasta        | bridge          | scrabble |

