.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, musician, lawyer, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, taxi, trike
1. the dancer is between the electrician and the person driving the boat##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the dancer##3
4. the musician is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
6. the lawyer is not the person driving the taxi##6
7. the electrician is not to the right of the lawyer##8
8. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | electrician   | dancer | lawyer | musician |
| Transport     | trike | bus       | boat  | taxi    |

