2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person who likes coral##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes black and the person who likes fuchsia##2

.:: Answer ::.
