.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, grapefruit, peas
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, lemonade, juice
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking juice is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade | almond-milk   | cola    |

