.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, may, december
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in february##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in december and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Birthday   | november | december      | may     | february     |

 